	description = "Roa'sara, in the Qrri'terr system, is a small, militarized planet housing the city-state of Tri'sorr. Since its founding 200 years ago, Roa'sara has been in a state of constant defense against incursions from a species known only as the Hrud. This ongoing conflict has led to a heavy Raskinta presence and strong cooperation with its military allies. Roa'sara's primary exports include rare minerals and it maintains a robust defense industry."
